Oh!

17
00:00:39,963 --> 00:00:41,463
It's been
a while, sir

18
00:00:41,563 --> 00:00:43,529
I just made contact
with Alnus.

19
00:00:43,629 --> 00:00:45,229
They said they would
be able to accept all

20
00:00:45,329 --> 00:00:47,663
the people you picked
up along the way.

21
