a personal request of Grey's.

30
00:01:04,863 --> 00:01:09,063
He's Pin's subordinate.
And I've accepted the task, sir.

31
00:01:09,163 --> 00:01:10,963
Looks like you've
already made up your mind

32
00:01:11,063 --> 00:01:13,096
with or without our
help haven't ya.

33
00:01:13,563 --> 00:01:14,463
Come in!

34
00:01:14,563 --> 00:01:14,663
Huh?

35
00:01:14,763 --> 00:01:15,696
Reporting!

36
00:01:15,796 --> 00:01:17,096
Uh...
ah! Uh...

37
00:01:17,196 --> 00:01:18,163
Reporting!

38
00:01:18,263 --> 00:01:18,629
Reporting!

39
00:01:18,729 --> 00:01:19,929
Reporting!

40
00:01:20,029 --> 00:01:22,296
It's good to see
you back... soldier!

41
00:01:22,396 --> 00:01:23,896
What the heck's
going on?!

42
00:01:23,996 --> 00:01:24,329
Aw!

43
00:01:24,429 --> 00:01:25,496
You didn't think
you were going

44
00:01:25,596 --> 00:01:26,863
on this mission
without us did ya?

45
00:01:26,963 --> 00:01:30,163
I'm a little hurt
I didn't get a call

46
00:01:30,263 --> 00:01:32,029
when you were about
to get into a fight. ,/
Remember, I'm always
here to help.

47
00:01:32,129 --> 00:01:34,196
Just let me know
what I can do okay?

48
00:01:34,296 --> 00:01:36,463
