You know you can
always count on us, sir.

50
00:01:38,529 --> 00:01:40,296
Aw.. you guys're
the best!

51
00:01:40,396 --> 00:01:41,196
Let's do this!

52
00:01:41,296 --> 00:01:42,329
Ah...

53
00:01:43,663 --> 00:01:46,029
Alright. So here's
what we're gonna do.

54
00:01:46,129 --> 00:01:48,029
We need Rory and Lelei
in the Palace.

55
00:01:48,129 --> 00:01:49,696
I will disguise
myself as a footman

56
00:01:49,796 --> 00:01:51,396
and walk them through
the front gate.

57
00:01:51,496 --> 00:01:55,163
Kurata and Kuribayashi follow
Tuka, and infiltrate the rear.

58
00:01:55,263 --> 00:01:57,896
Tuka, I want you to
use your slumber magic.

59
00:01:57,996 --> 00:02:00,563
Tomita, you and the old man
will cover our escape.

60
00:02:00,663 --> 00:02:02,163
No problem, chief

61
00:02:02,263 --> 00:02:04,763
Kurokawa and Yao
