Yes, it has an M2.

74
00:02:29,596 --> 00:02:31,163
I can handle the
hand‐to‐hand combat!

75
00:02:31,263 --> 00:02:35,229
Heh. Well, the
main objective will be
to rescue the prisoners, but...

76
00:02:35,329 --> 00:02:37,696
If that dumbass prince
does something stupid again,

77
00:02:37,796 --> 00:02:38,896
have at it.

78
00:02:38,996 --> 00:02:40,196
(growls)

79
