80
00:02:41,263 --> 00:02:43,596
But, Sir. Why would
they let you in?

81
00:02:43,696 --> 00:02:46,096
Even with Rory and Lelei
accompanying you.

82
00:02:46,196 --> 00:02:49,529
I'm sure they must be watching
out for the JSDF presence.

83
00:02:49,629 --> 00:02:50,729
Oh they won't...

84
00:02:50,829 --> 00:02:53,096
I won't be going in
as a man in uniform.

85
00:02:53,196 --> 00:02:54,796
Itami:
They won't even see us comin'.

86
00:02:54,896 --> 00:02:56,663
