102
00:03:27,629 --> 00:03:31,196
We have been summoned by the
Prince to the Imperial Palace.

103
00:03:31,296 --> 00:03:33,729
Villager:
So you carrying some
precious cargo or something?

104
00:03:33,829 --> 00:03:35,296
That's gotta be
some rough work.

105
00:03:35,396 --> 00:03:36,429
Itami:
You have no idea...

106
00:03:36,529 --> 00:03:37,463
(giggles)

107
00:03:37,563 --> 00:03:38,663
State your
business.

108
00:03:38,763 --> 00:03:40,496
Guard 1:
The Palace is
under strict guard.

109
00:03:40,596 --> 00:03:43,296
Guard 2:
We cannot allow anyone
through without permission.

110
00:03:43,396 --> 00:03:46,929
I am Lelei la Lalena‐
I'm from the Coda Village.

111
00:03:47,029 --> 00:03:49,063
The Prince has requested
our presence here.

112
00:03:49,163 --> 00:03:50,296
Please tell him
we've arrived.

113
00:03:50,396 --> 00:03:52,629
We've been told he
would like to speak to us

114
00:03:52,729 --> 00:03:54,363
about defeating
the flame dragon.

115
00:03:54,463 --> 00:03:56,129
Oh, so you're
the ones?!

116
00:03:56,229 --> 00:03:57,929
Please... Please
excuse us, my ladies!

117
00:03:58,029 --> 00:03:59,329
Here's our
invitation.

118
00:03:59,429 --> 00:03:59,896
Right!
Right!

119
00:03:59,996 --> 00:04:01,329
Guard 1:
Hey, footman!

120
00:04:01,429 --> 00:04:02,163
Don't be an idiot.

121
00:04:02,263 --> 00:04:04,196
You can't leave your wagon
blocking the gate!

122
00:04:04,296 --> 00:04:05,363
Bring it inside!

123
00:04:05,463 --> 00:04:07,129
Yes, sir! But I...

124
00:04:07,229 --> 00:04:09,496
Come on in, please!
Right this way!

125
00:04:09,596 --> 00:04:10,329
Make yourself
at home.

126
00:04:10,429 --> 00:04:11,296
Rory:
Thank you,
darling.

127
00:04:11,396 --> 00:04:13,296
Hey! You guys?!

128
00:04:13,396 --> 00:04:13,963
(groans)

129
00:04:14,063 --> 00:04:17,436
Do I still have to drag this
by myself? Who's plan was this?

130
00:04:17,873 --> 00:04:20,563
Hang in there.
You got this, chief.

131
00:04:27,473 --> 00:04:29,307
Ahh! Ahh!

132
00:04:29,407 --> 00:04:30,273
Ah!

133
00:04:34,873 --> 00:04:36,407
What do you
want from me?

134
00:04:36,507 --> 00:04:40,040
I think you already
know that, Princess.

135
00:04:40,140 --> 00:04:42,373
The Order of the Rose
were only following the orders

136
00:04:42,473 --> 00:04:44,207
given by the
Emperor himself.

137
00:04:44,307 --> 00:04:46,607
So are you saying that allowing
the enemy to get inside

138
00:04:46,707 --> 00:04:49,640
the Imperial Capital
was the Emperor's idea?

139
00:04:49,740 --> 00:04:50,207
Huh?

140
00:04:50,307 --> 00:04:52,940
Helm:
Are you feigning
ignorance?

141
00:04:53,040 --> 00:04:56,840
(hysterical laughter)

142
00:04:56,940 --> 00:05:01,273
What's so funny?
Your knights helped the enemy
infiltrate our lands.

143
00:05:01,373 --> 00:05:03,407
You created the
situation we're in!

144
00:05:03,507 --> 00:05:06,807
If that isn't treason,
then what is?!

145
00:05:06,907 --> 00:05:08,207
Tell me, if they're
not guilty,

146
00:05:08,307 --> 00:05:09,740
then why would they
flee the Capital?!

147
00:05:09,840 --> 00:05:12,640
Helm:
They're running away because
they have something to hide!

148
00:05:12,740 --> 00:05:13,440
(laughs)

149
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:16,007
Do I really need to
spell it out for you?

150
00:05:16,107 --> 00:05:18,140
It's because they know
that if they stay,

151
00:05:18,240 --> 00:05:20,040
they'll be treated
like this.

152
00:05:20,140 --> 00:05:21,907
If you run away, you're a
traitor.

153
00:05:22,007 --> 00:05:24,907
If you don't, then you're just
a traitor who's up to something.

154
00:05:25,007 --> 00:05:27,707
You're arrogance
won't change anything!

155
00:05:27,807 --> 00:05:31,507
You have given us
up before we've even
gotten started, Princess.

156
00:05:31,607 --> 00:05:34,340
Prince Zorzal.
What do we do with her?

157
00:05:38,673 --> 00:05:46,940
Rory:
They look so peaceful.
Almost... dead.

158
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:49,007
Lelei:
Every guard in the hallway
should be out for awhile. ,/
This is Itami.
We're inside.

159
00:05:49,107 --> 00:05:50,840
Itami:
How's it going
over there? Over.

160
00:05:50,940 --> 00:05:54,407
This is Kuribayashi.
We have made it into the Palace.

161
00:05:54,507 --> 00:05:56,773
Shino:
Tuka put the guards
to sleep. Over.

162
00:05:56,873 --> 00:05:59,107
(chuckles)
Hello...

163
00:05:59,207 --> 00:05:59,507
Who are you?!

164
00:05:59,607 --> 00:06:02,307
