if you want to stay alive.

175
00:06:27,806 --> 00:06:29,240
Very good.

176
00:06:31,106 --> 00:06:32,473
What am I do with you?

177
00:06:32,573 --> 00:06:35,106
I have complete faith that you
would never even think about

178
00:06:35,206 --> 00:06:36,740
abandoning the Empire.

179
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:40,373
But it is a fact that the Order
of the Rose assisted the enemy.

180
00:06:40,473 --> 00:06:42,506
I know nothing of that!

181
00:06:42,606 --> 00:06:45,406
That's enough. ,/
That's not even what
I care about anymore.

182
00:06:45,506 --> 00:06:47,740
My priorities have
recently changed.

183
00:06:47,840 --> 00:06:50,506
What I want now is
to defeat our enemies!

184
00:06:50,606 --> 00:06:52,473
And be an
all‐powerful ruler!

185
00:06:52,573 --> 00:06:54,373
If they wish to proceed
with the peace talks,

186
00:06:54,473 --> 00:06:56,206
they will have
to come here.

187
00:06:56,306 --> 00:06:57,406
Zorzal:
So don't worry.

188
00:06:57,506 --> 00:06:59,840
Until then, I will
need you alive.

189
00:06:59,940 --> 00:07:02,473
And by the time they arrive
we will have regrouped...

190
00:07:02,573 --> 00:07:04,873
and prepared ourselves
a counterattack for them!

191
00:07:04,973 --> 00:07:07,706
We've been taming a giant ogre
just for the occasion!

192
00:07:07,806 --> 00:07:10,673
They can attack us whenever
they please. Bring it on!

193
00:07:10,773 --> 00:07:11,073
Rory:
Oh really?

194
00:07:11,173 --> 00:07:12,740
Oh!
Rory:
Oh really?

195
00:07:12,840 --> 00:07:13,640
(gasps)

196
00:07:18,273 --> 00:07:19,906
Rory:
(giggles)

197
00:07:20,006 --> 00:07:21,306
Hmm...

198
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,306
