202
00:07:34,673 --> 00:07:37,906
Princess Pina. We are here
to rescue you.

203
00:07:42,840 --> 00:07:45,140
Oh! Stay Away! ,/
You there! What are
you guards doing?!

204
00:07:45,240 --> 00:07:47,340
Do not let them
come anywhere near me!

205
00:07:47,440 --> 00:07:49,073
Your elite
soldiers outside

206
00:07:49,173 --> 00:07:50,873
