wise soldiers.

213
00:08:04,540 --> 00:08:09,840
(growls)
You are going to die!
Ogaaaare! Get in here!

214
00:08:09,940 --> 00:08:12,840
Come and tear
these bastards apart!

215
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:15,073
(monsterous breathing)

216
00:08:15,173 --> 00:08:16,140
Huh?

217
00:08:16,240 --> 00:08:16,273
Huh?!

218
00:08:16,373 --> 00:08:17,373
Ah!
Huh?!

219
00:08:17,473 --> 00:08:19,206
Zorzal you've lost
your mind!

220
00:08:19,306 --> 00:08:20,973
I no longer
have a choice.

221
00:08:21,073 --> 00:08:22,906
