231
00:08:55,506 --> 00:08:56,906
(pained roar)
(ecstatic moan)

232
00:08:57,006 --> 00:08:57,840
(pained roar)
Mmm...

233
00:08:57,940 --> 00:08:59,440
(pained roar)

234
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:01,340
(agonized roar)
(giggles)

235
00:09:01,440 --> 00:09:05,740
(agonized roaring continues)

236
00:09:13,673 --> 00:09:15,540
