the royal princess.

244
00:09:30,906 --> 00:09:32,806
Come on. Time to go.

245
00:09:33,840 --> 00:09:34,506
Itami, I...

246
00:09:34,606 --> 00:09:38,840
Heh. Remember we're the
self defense force that cares.

247
00:09:38,940 --> 00:09:39,440
The good guys.

248
00:09:39,540 --> 00:09:46,106
Hold it! It's not over
between you and me!

249
00:09:46,206 --> 00:09:46,940
Let's go! Just the two of us,
I'll take you all by myself. ,/
Wha‐

250
00:09:48,906 --> 00:09:50,173
No matter where you are,

251
00:09:50,273 --> 00:09:52,206
you'll always be
within our sights.

252
00:09:52,306 --> 00:09:54,940
You step out of line
and we will drop you.

253
00:09:55,040 --> 00:09:58,640
Itami:
I'll say it again.
You will stop going after Lelei.

254
00:09:58,740 --> 00:10:01,773
And you'll give
us Princess Pina.

255
00:10:01,873 --> 00:10:05,306
Otherwise, next time,
a bullet is going right
through your skull.

256
00:10:05,406 --> 00:10:07,940
Do you understand what
I'm telling you?

257
00:10:08,806 --> 00:10:10,740
Uh...

258
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:13,973
Alright... let's go.

259
00:10:30,010 --> 00:10:30,985
Hey Chief!
You need a ride?!

260
00:10:31,085 --> 00:10:32,385
Right on time!

261
00:10:32,485 --> 00:10:36,018
Uh Rory... You don't
have to sit on my lap!

262
00:10:36,118 --> 00:10:37,585
Plenty of room
in the back!

263
00:10:37,685 --> 00:10:38,485
Oh. What?

264
00:10:38,585 --> 00:10:41,218
But we'll be picking up some
other people too, right?

265
00:10:41,318 --> 00:10:42,585
I don't like
being crowded.

266
00:10:42,685 --> 00:10:45,785
Oh come on! I see nothing
has changed has it?!

267
00:10:45,885 --> 00:10:47,285
I am not enjoying this!

268
00:10:47,385 --> 00:10:49,685
Now. What's the status
of the others?

269
00:10:49,785 --> 00:10:50,485
Okay so...

270
00:10:50,585 --> 00:10:53,252
Kuribayashi's already
engaged in a firefight.

271
00:10:53,352 --> 00:10:55,018
There aren't really
all that many of them,

272
00:10:55,118 --> 00:10:57,785
but Tuka's magic
won't last much longer.

273
00:10:57,885 --> 00:11:01,552
Kurata:
And as for Kurokawa...

274
00:11:01,652 --> 00:11:03,685
This is Kurokawa.
We have the Emperor with us. ,/
His vitals
are looking good!

275
00:11:03,785 --> 00:11:04,818
Roger that!

276
00:11:04,918 --> 00:11:06,285
(battle cries)

277
00:11:06,385 --> 00:11:07,152
Get out of the way!

278
00:11:07,252 --> 00:11:09,218
(battle cries)

279
00:11:12,452 --> 00:11:14,552
Move it you dummies! ,/
Getting hit by a
car really hurts!

280
00:11:14,652 --> 00:11:16,218
Ahhh!

281
00:11:18,718 --> 00:11:21,818
Tuka, Kuribayashi!
Get in the back!

282
00:11:21,918 --> 00:11:22,352
Kurata!

283
00:11:22,452 --> 00:11:24,352
Kurata:
Moving out!

284
00:11:24,452 --> 00:11:27,552
Itami:
Kurokawa. We just collected
Tuka and Kuribayashi.

285
00:11:27,652 --> 00:11:28,918
We're on our way
to get you.

286
00:11:29,018 --> 00:11:30,818
Mari:
Roger that.

287
00:11:30,918 --> 00:11:33,718
When they get here, we'll be
able to move the Emperor.

288
00:11:33,818 --> 00:11:34,952
I understand!

289
00:11:35,052 --> 00:11:36,252
It's my
greatest honor...

290
00:11:36,352 --> 00:11:38,952
to protect Princess Pina
and Emperor Molto.

291
00:11:39,052 --> 00:11:41,218
If necessary,
I will gladly be the bait!

292
00:11:41,318 --> 00:11:43,118
There won't be
any need for that.

293
00:11:43,218 --> 00:11:45,785
You can trust we will
take care of them.

294
00:11:46,552 --> 00:11:48,252
Great! Everyone's here!

295
00:11:48,352 --> 00:11:50,085
Hang on this is
gonna be close!

296
00:11:50,185 --> 00:11:51,585
(nervous groan)

297
00:11:51,685 --> 00:11:53,218
All:
(scream)

298
00:11:54,052 --> 00:11:56,352
(screaming continues)

299
00:11:58,518 --> 00:12:01,452
Kurata:
Aagh! We're not gonna make it!

300
00:12:01,552 --> 00:12:02,452
Ahh!

301
00:12:02,552 --> 00:12:05,452
Grr... what WAS that?!

302
00:12:07,052 --> 00:12:09,218
Gotta clear passage
for you, Chief!

303
00:12:11,252 --> 00:12:12,518
(panicked panting)

304
00:12:12,618 --> 00:12:14,118
Don't shoot on the city streets.

305
00:12:14,218 --> 00:12:16,985
We don't want any of the stray
rounds to hit the civilians!

306
00:12:17,085 --> 00:12:19,752
Tomita:
If we can get through the castle
gate, then we can stop them.

307
00:12:19,852 --> 00:12:21,918
Kuwabara:
Well... then we better make it.

308
00:12:22,018 --> 00:12:22,885
You hear that?!

309
00:12:22,985 --> 00:12:23,818
Yes, sir!

310
00:12:23,918 --> 00:12:24,318
Hooah!

311
00:12:24,418 --> 00:12:26,252
Sweeper:
Don't let them through!

312
00:12:28,052 --> 00:12:30,185
Dammit! They're
moving too fast!

313
00:12:31,485 --> 00:12:33,152
Tomita:
We're at the west gate!

314
00:12:33,252 --> 00:12:34,352
Keep advancing.

315
00:12:34,452 --> 00:12:35,785
Itami:
Copy!

316
00:12:35,885 --> 00:12:38,185
(battle cries)

317
00:12:38,285 --> 00:12:39,918
These guys don't ever give up!

318
00:12:42,052 --> 00:12:43,485
Special Forces:
Ready to fire.

319
00:12:44,085 --> 00:12:45,285
Archer:
Fire!

320
00:12:46,885 --> 00:12:48,318
(soldiers screaming)

321
00:12:52,318 --> 00:12:54,852
(struggling)

322
00:12:54,952 --> 00:12:56,652
That took care of 'em!

323
00:12:56,752 --> 00:12:57,385
Yeah we did it!

324
00:12:57,485 --> 00:13:00,018
I love it when a
plan comes together!

325
00:13:00,118 --> 00:13:01,552
(relieved sigh)

326
00:13:01,652 --> 00:13:02,885
Princess Pina.

327
00:13:02,985 --> 00:13:04,385
Hi, Hamilton.

328
00:13:04,485 --> 00:13:07,585
I'm so glad you're safe.
Your Highness...

329
00:13:07,685 --> 00:13:09,985
If anything awful would have
happened to you,

330
00:13:10,085 --> 00:13:12,118
I would have just died!

331
00:13:12,218 --> 00:13:14,352
I'm sorry if
I frightened you.

332
00:13:16,318 --> 00:13:18,285
Pina:
Oh father...

333
00:13:18,385 --> 00:13:19,585
I appreciate this.

334
00:13:19,685 --> 00:13:22,518
I can't thank you enough
for rescuing the Emperor.

335
00:13:22,618 --> 00:13:25,252
I take it ‐ he was
the top priority.

336
00:13:25,352 --> 00:13:28,018
I guess it's blind luck
you found me as well.

337
00:13:28,118 --> 00:13:29,185
Not at all.

338
00:13:29,285 --> 00:13:30,818
My primary objective
of this mission

339
00:13:30,918 --> 00:13:34,185
was to get you out and
someplace safe, Princess Pina.

340
00:13:34,285 --> 00:13:36,418
After that, if we were able
to find the Emperor,

341
00:13:36,518 --> 00:13:37,585
then we were
to extract him.

342
00:13:37,685 --> 00:13:39,385
Saving the Emperor
was secondary?!

343
00:13:39,485 --> 00:13:43,285
Itami:
Yes. That came as a
direct order from my boss.

344
00:13:43,385 --> 00:13:45,318
That if we're going in
to save the princess,

345
00:13:45,418 --> 00:13:47,985
then we would need to rescue
the Emperor, as well.

346
00:13:48,085 --> 00:13:49,385
What's the
ulterior motive?

347
00:13:49,485 --> 00:13:51,152
We need to be seen
as an alliance.

348
00:13:51,252 --> 00:13:54,052
If you are joined by
the Emperor and the
pro‐peace representatives...

349
00:13:54,152 --> 00:13:58,352
Then we can show that there is
only one traitor within
the Imperial regime.

350
00:13:58,452 --> 00:13:58,985
Your Majesty!

351
00:13:59,085 --> 00:14:00,018
Father!
Your Majesty!

352
00:14:00,118 --> 00:14:01,952
Are you all right...
Your Highness?

353
00:14:02,052 --> 00:14:05,185
Yes. Despite the
exceedingly bumpy ride.

354
00:14:05,285 --> 00:14:08,052
I do believe that
I'm doing rather well.

355
00:14:08,152 --> 00:14:09,452
I'm glad you're OK.

356
00:14:09,552 --> 00:14:13,885
And the Senate representatives
have all been successfully
evacuated to Italica.

357
00:14:13,985 --> 00:14:17,552
Itami:
At our current speed,
we should get there tomorrow.

358
00:14:17,652 --> 00:14:20,352
On horseback that always
took us several days,

359
00:14:20,452 --> 00:14:23,252
but with this contraption
our world has gotten smaller.

360
00:14:23,352 --> 00:14:24,652
Truly incredible.

361
00:14:24,752 --> 00:14:25,185
Father!

362
00:14:25,285 --> 00:14:28,418
Zorzal is trying to create mass
confusion within the country.

363
00:14:28,518 --> 00:14:31,818
Stop him! Please speak with him
and make him listen to reason.

364
00:14:31,918 --> 00:14:34,352
There's no point in my
going back to the capital.

365
00:14:34,452 --> 00:14:39,318
Your brother won't even
pretend to listen to what
I have to say anymore anyway.

366
00:14:39,418 --> 00:14:43,285
No, I think it's best if we go
along with Japan's plot.

367
00:14:43,918 --> 00:14:45,118
What plot?

368
00:14:45,218 --> 00:14:47,418
Civil war is
now inevitable.

369
00:14:47,518 --> 00:14:51,818
Pina... I'm making you the
Crown Princess of the Empire.

370
00:14:51,918 --> 00:14:53,818
What? You want me?

371
00:14:53,918 --> 00:14:54,718
Yes, my dear.

372
00:14:54,818 --> 00:14:57,918
I want you to be
the voice to establish
a legitimate government,

373
00:14:58,018 --> 00:15:00,585
And to lead the opposition
against your brother.

374
00:15:00,685 --> 00:15:03,152
No, father! I cannot
go against him!

375
00:15:03,252 --> 00:15:04,352
It will be up to you.

376
00:15:04,452 --> 00:15:07,452
The choice will be yours
to do what you think is best.

377
00:15:07,552 --> 00:15:09,352
Molto:
You can seek to
make peace with him,

378
00:15:09,452 --> 00:15:12,452
or you can divide the
Empire in two.

379
00:15:14,785 --> 00:15:18,852
The time is now. You are
the one to decide our future.

380
00:15:33,985 --> 00:15:37,452
Tell me... where are we
planning to go, Your Highness?

381
00:15:37,552 --> 00:15:40,618
To the Northeast for now.
We'll figure out the rest later.

382
00:15:40,718 --> 00:15:44,085
But, sir. If we leave
the Imperial Capital,

383
00:15:44,185 --> 00:15:46,052
We will lose control
of the country.

384
00:15:46,152 --> 00:15:46,818
(growls)

385
00:15:46,918 --> 00:15:47,852
Shut your mouth!

386
00:15:47,952 --> 00:15:48,618
(gunshot)

387
00:15:48,718 --> 00:15:49,918
Oh!

388
00:15:50,018 --> 00:15:51,252
(whimpers)

389
00:15:56,418 --> 00:15:57,318
It's Furuta here.

390
00:15:57,418 --> 00:16:01,252
Prince Zorzal is escaping
with the nobles and the
pro‐war representatives.

391
00:16:01,352 --> 00:16:04,285
He's leaving the capital.
I'm not sure where yet.

392
00:16:04,385 --> 00:16:06,618
Following them will be too risky
so hang tight for now.

393
00:16:06,718 --> 00:16:09,385
I'm going to keep
my distance. Over 'n out.

394
00:16:10,718 --> 00:16:11,785
What she up to?

395
00:16:11,885 --> 00:16:14,718
Thule:
I endured the life
of a prisoner

396
00:16:14,818 --> 00:16:18,618
to take revenge for my
country that they destroyed.

397
00:16:19,618 --> 00:16:22,485
No matter what
the cost may be.

398
00:16:22,585 --> 00:16:25,518
I vowed the Empire be
obliterated.

399
00:16:25,618 --> 00:16:29,585
That was my only wish,
and I have finally achieved it.

400
00:16:31,018 --> 00:16:32,852
But.. why?

401
00:16:35,052 --> 00:16:37,818
Why is it that
I can't stop crying?

402
00:16:37,918 --> 00:16:39,418
Godammitah...

403
00:16:39,518 --> 00:16:42,752
This cannot be
happening to me...

404
00:16:42,852 --> 00:16:43,585
(gunshot)

405
00:16:43,685 --> 00:16:44,385
(cowers)

406
00:16:44,485 --> 00:16:48,985
I swear to you...
I will have my revenge!

407
00:16:49,085 --> 00:16:53,252
Lelei:
Ten days later, a grand
ceremony was held in Italica.

408
00:16:53,352 --> 00:16:55,818
Princess Pina was named
the Crown Princess,

409
00:16:55,918 --> 00:17:00,352
and a new, legitimate
government of the Empire
was officially founded.

410
00:17:35,252 --> 00:17:41,018
My dearest daughter Pina,
From this day forward...,
I do hereby...

411
00:17:41,118 --> 00:17:44,085
entrust the Empire's
government to you.

412
00:17:44,185 --> 00:17:46,452
The realm is yours to rule.

413
00:17:47,385 --> 00:17:50,718
Take good care...
of our country.

414
00:17:50,818 --> 00:17:53,018
Your time is now... Pina.

415
00:17:53,118 --> 00:17:54,685
(fighting tears)

416
00:17:56,152 --> 00:17:58,985
My heart and soul...
are true to the Empire.

417
00:17:59,085 --> 00:18:03,252
And I swear... I will lead
this country to prosperity,

418
00:18:03,352 --> 00:18:05,452
in peace with Japan!

419
00:18:21,852 --> 00:18:23,018
This is so great!

420
00:18:23,118 --> 00:18:24,685
I was hoping
for a happy ending!

421
00:18:24,785 --> 00:18:28,018
Are you actually crying?
Not cool dude!

422
00:18:28,118 --> 00:18:30,852
Huh? Whatever, this is
the greatest day ever!

423
00:18:30,952 --> 00:18:31,885
(sobbing)

424
00:18:31,985 --> 00:18:33,518
Hey, baby...
Are you ok?

425
00:18:33,618 --> 00:18:34,718
Yeah.
Well, what is this?

426
00:18:34,818 --> 00:18:35,552
Well, what is this?

427
00:18:35,652 --> 00:18:36,385
Oh!

428
00:18:36,885 --> 00:18:37,452
(chuckles)

429
00:18:37,552 --> 00:18:38,352
We've been seeing
each other...

430
00:18:38,452 --> 00:18:43,318
We're kinduv a thing now ‐
Ever since I was sent back
to Japan awhile back.

431
00:18:43,418 --> 00:18:47,218
I couldn't say anything before,
but we're expecting a baby...

432
00:18:47,318 --> 00:18:50,385
And... we've recently gotten to
know each other as well.

433
00:18:50,485 --> 00:18:53,185
We kinda overcame uh...
the language barrier.

434
00:18:53,285 --> 00:18:56,018
You got hurt because of
my personal vendetta.

435
00:18:56,118 --> 00:18:57,385
Yes, I did.

436
00:18:57,485 --> 00:19:00,218
You better take care of me...
until I get better.

437
00:19:00,318 --> 00:19:01,085
I think I can do that.

438
00:19:01,185 --> 00:19:04,918
The love between Sugawara
and I... will last forever!

439
00:19:05,018 --> 00:19:07,518
Yeah, uh... And it will
all be totally legal I swear!

440
00:19:07,618 --> 00:19:10,218
What?! When did
all this happen?!

441
00:19:10,318 --> 00:19:11,185
This is
not fair!

442
00:19:11,285 --> 00:19:14,485
Hey! Why does everybody suddenly
have a sweetheart except me?!

443
00:19:14,585 --> 00:19:17,118
Because you're easily fooled
and a little bit nuts.

444
00:19:17,218 --> 00:19:19,552
That wasn't niiiice...

445
00:19:19,652 --> 00:19:20,385
Oh... Wait!

446
00:19:20,485 --> 00:19:23,052
I just realized the chief
isn't here to celebrate.

447
00:19:23,152 --> 00:19:24,718
Where... is he?

448
00:19:24,818 --> 00:19:25,485
Yeah he's not here.

449
00:19:25,585 --> 00:19:26,518
Uh... No shit.

450
00:19:26,618 --> 00:19:27,585
Okay soo...

451
00:19:27,685 --> 00:19:31,318
You know how he feels
about all his otaku
hobbies and everything?

452
00:19:31,418 --> 00:19:33,918
Well he sorta
had somewhere to be.

453
00:19:36,218 --> 00:19:40,818
Yeaaaahhhh... I'm back, BABY!

454
00:19:40,918 --> 00:19:44,252
It's been too long.
Can't believe it's been a year!

455
00:19:44,352 --> 00:19:48,885
Finally the event
I've been dreaming about!

456
00:19:49,818 --> 00:19:50,818
OHHHH! I love you!
(kisses the cover) ,/
Sorry, Princess Pina!

457
00:19:50,918 --> 00:19:53,752
I just... I just could
nots let an opportunity

458
00:19:53,852 --> 00:19:54,918
like this pass me by!

459
00:19:55,018 --> 00:19:59,852
Event Staff:
The doujinshi exhibition
and sales is cancelled!
Itami:

460
00:20:01,252 --> 00:20:04,585
Hoo‐hoo‐haa‐haah!
I'm finally here!

461
00:20:04,685 --> 00:20:06,552
And if we don't put
an end to it right now...

462
00:20:06,652 --> 00:20:09,318
THEY'LL SHUT DOWN
THE COMIC'S CONVENTION!

463
00:20:09,418 --> 00:20:11,818
Man, I things have been
a little bit crazy lately.

464
00:20:11,918 --> 00:20:13,718
But I'll just leave
that in the past.

465
00:20:13,818 --> 00:20:17,852
Because what's really
important... is the future!

466
00:20:17,952 --> 00:20:19,885
Guh! Ahhh!

467
00:20:20,885 --> 00:20:24,452
That hurt...!
Why are you guys here?!

468
00:20:24,552 --> 00:20:27,485
It's not very fair if you're
the only one having fun, Daddy.

469
00:20:27,585 --> 00:20:30,452
Itami, will you please
take me to the bookstore?

470
00:20:30,552 --> 00:20:31,352
How did you get here?!

471
00:20:31,452 --> 00:20:35,752
We asked the delightfully
mustachioed Hazama for
permission to visit.

472
00:20:35,852 --> 00:20:39,185
But only under the strict
condition, that you would
take care of us.

473
00:20:39,285 --> 00:20:41,718
Uh What?! Why does
he hate me?

474
00:20:41,818 --> 00:20:45,118
Look here. I'm sorry but
I have some important business.

475
00:20:45,218 --> 00:20:46,985
Please, just go
back to Alnus.

476
00:20:47,085 --> 00:20:48,285
(crowd chattering)

477
00:20:48,385 --> 00:20:49,952
Male Bystander 1:
Is that who
I think it is...?!

478
00:20:50,052 --> 00:20:50,852
Male Bystander 2:
Oh my gosh!

479
00:20:50,952 --> 00:20:51,952
Hey Rory!

480
00:20:52,052 --> 00:20:52,985
They're really real!

481
00:20:53,085 --> 00:20:54,518
Hey!

482
00:20:54,618 --> 00:20:55,052
Hey there!

483
00:20:55,152 --> 00:20:56,285
Wow, that's really Rory!

484
00:20:56,385 --> 00:20:58,252
Gotta get her autograph!

485
00:21:00,252 --> 00:21:02,185
(crowd intensifies)

486
00:21:03,685 --> 00:21:05,252
Hey look over here!
Lemmie get a picture!

487
00:21:05,352 --> 00:21:07,185
There are so many
people here!

488
00:21:07,285 --> 00:21:08,818
And the crowd is growing.

489
00:21:08,918 --> 00:21:09,852
Of course it is,

490
00:21:09,952 --> 00:21:13,152
I'm sure we'll get lots of
attention everywhere we go.

491
00:21:13,252 --> 00:21:16,518
Oh God... This is going
from bad to worse...

492
00:21:16,618 --> 00:21:18,418
Hey! You there!
What's going on?!

493
00:21:18,518 --> 00:21:21,252
Wait! This is
just uh... I swear!

494
00:21:21,352 --> 00:21:23,618
Whatever it is, you're gonna
have to come with me!

495
00:21:23,718 --> 00:21:24,218
Huh?

496
00:21:24,318 --> 00:21:25,452
Don't worry, son.

497
00:21:25,552 --> 00:21:28,152
Uh... I'll take
ya someplace safe, 'kay?

498
00:21:28,252 --> 00:21:29,752
Uh yeah, no thanks.

499
00:21:29,852 --> 00:21:33,252
Officer:
Just get in the car.
You're gonna be fine.

500
00:21:34,018 --> 00:21:34,685
Is this Hell...?

501
00:21:34,785 --> 00:21:39,018
When I, feel low!
One place to‐

502
00:21:39,118 --> 00:21:40,018
AAAAAAHHHH!

503
